<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>101</hymn_number>
<author>V. Hawla</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khawvel ahin malzin ka hi,
 Aw ka ngai sek ngei ie ka inkuonte;
 Ka cham sung hin buoina tinchengte'n,
 Tuilien bang' nicheng in ei tawk.

[V2]
 Aw hun ei daltu hi a beih tieng leh,
 Mundet lam chu zuon ta'ng ka;
 Ziechun ngailo in ka chenna hi,
 Buoina cheng tawh pawtsan tang ka.

[V3]
 2. Lungkham dak gi thangvelte leh,
 Buoina tincheng thawm gi ka zakte hin;
 Ka kumsawt gam ei ngaihsak zawdiek,
 Ka Pa mel ni bang a vakna.

[V4]
 3. Ka zinna gam thalek ahin,
 Ka Lal gam lutpih tak ka nei puoh ie;
 Hinna thu vaithak nei ki vang le'ng,
 Khutngawn in ka gam zuon ing ka.

[V5]
 4. Ka Lalgam chun ni a ngai puoi,
 A melhawih na'n khawpi sung a salhvak;
 Vaihawmna Lal chutphah chunga chu'n,
 Pahchakna gihawih te'n a bawm.</lyrics>
<title>Khawvel Ahin Malzin Ka Hi</title>
</song>